item.title: SomeType (Type alias)
item.description: SomeType Type: Alias Description No description provided Information The type SomeType is defined as an alias to the primitive type String within the region Everything. This alias was defined in the RIDDL source file ‘everything.riddl’ like so: type SomeType is String
